## Iterative Graphics


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="1,11|2|3,4|5,6,7|8,9,10"}
plot_density <- function(data, var, grp = "") {
  ggplot(data, aes(x = !!sym(var))) +
    geom_density(aes(fill = !!sym(grp)), position = "identity",
                 color = "grey30", alpha = .3) +
    coord_cartesian(expand = FALSE, clip = "off") +
    scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::label_number()) +
    scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Dark2", name = NULL) +
    theme(legend.position = "top")
}
```
:::



## Iterative Graphics


::: {.cell output-location='column'}

```{.r .cell-code}
